data.description: This four bedroom, three bath home is perfect for families or individuals looking for privacy and convenience. The highlight of this home is the large kitchen with high ceilings and a skylight, creating an airy and bright atmosphere. The kitchen is equipped with granite countertops and pull-out features that make cooking a breeze. Upstairs, you will find three bedrooms and two full bathrooms, offering ample space for relaxation and rest. One unique feature of this home is the option to have a mother-in-law suite downstairs. This provides flexibility to accommodate extended family members or can be used as a short-term rental for added income. Whether you're looking for a space to welcome guests or generate extra revenue, this home offers versatility. Overall, this cozy home combines functionality, style, and potential income opportunities, making it an ideal choice for those seeking comfort and flexibility. 2023, NEW ROOF, NEW MINI SPLITS DOWNSTAIRS, NEW GARAGE DOOR. If you like golfing, fishing, hiking, swimming, fitness, pickleball, tennis, or your toes in the sand, call me today! HSV has it all! New buyers into HSV pay $1500.00 buy in fee to Hot Springs Village
